00:22:04,853 --> 00:22:09,417
Being flexible is really valuable anyway, because even when there's not whole studio change,

297
00:22:09,597 --> 00:22:13,561
there's often individual change. People's lives are moving around and changing all the time.

298
00:22:14,402 --> 00:22:19,947
And so creating flexibility so people know that they have space for those changes is really,

299
00:22:19,987 --> 00:22:24,471
really important to making them feel valued and like really important parts of the team.

300
00:22:26,055 --> 00:22:28,057
So allow people to make space in their lives.

301
00:22:29,138 --> 00:22:30,880
Flexible hours are really important.

302
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:35,524
I think they are a really easy way to fully empower your team

